-- MOVES-Deloitte names vice chairman for US investment management practice
-- 
-- Thu Aug 07, 2014 09:41AM EDT
-- None



Aug 7 (Reuters) - Patrick Henry, a partner with Deloitte & Touche LLP [DLTE.UL], has been appointed vice chairman and leader of the firm's investment management practice in the United States.

Henry, who has worked at Deloitte for 25 years, will be responsible for developing key sector initiatives across its audit, tax, consulting and advisory businesses.